any emotional preference.

441
00:33:17,119 --> 00:33:17,960
I understand.

442
00:33:18,740 --> 00:33:20,820
It's not something he can control.

443
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:23,680
Whether it's his first personality

444
00:33:23,680 --> 00:33:24,720
or his second,

445
00:33:26,680 --> 00:33:27,680
I won't blame him.

