00:40:16,679 --> 00:40:18,840
That's why your willingness
to cooperate is crucial.

563
00:40:20,559 --> 00:40:21,840
Can you just listen?

564
00:40:22,720 --> 00:40:23,800
If you work with us,

565
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:25,400
we'll do everything we can to help you.

566
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:27,120
How exactly am I supposed to cooperate?

567
00:40:28,880 --> 00:40:29,679
Kill him?

568
00:40:32,559 --> 00:40:34,400
Kill him in my own mind?

569
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:37,719
Make him die all over again?

570
00:40:37,719 --> 00:40:39,079
Liao Zhibai is dead.

571
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:42,039
He died ten years ago.

572
00:40:42,719 --> 00:40:44,199
There's no dying again.

573
00:40:44,280 --> 00:40:44,920
Shut up.

574
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:48,840
Everything about him

575
00:40:48,840 --> 00:40:50,920
exists only in your head.

576
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:54,960
You don't seriously believe
you can see ghosts, do you?

577
00:40:55,140 --> 00:40:57,400
Do you even believe it
yourself if you say it out loud?

578
00:41:00,060 --> 00:41:01,800
I don't care if he's
a person or a ghost.

579
00:41:03,679 --> 00:41:04,679
It doesn't matter to me.

580
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:08,079
All I know is

581
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:12,079
that when I was at my lowest,

582
00:41:13,199 --> 00:41:15,239
he was there.

583
00:41:16,079 --> 00:41:17,079
He stayed with me,

584
00:41:18,039 --> 00:41:18,880
and encouraged me.

585
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:23,800
Without him, I might
not have survived at all.

586
00:41:26,239 --> 00:41:29,119
I just want him to stay.

587
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:30,440
Is that so wrong?

588
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:35,840
This is the only way I can see him.

589
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:38,599
Why does everyone

590
00:41:38,599 --> 00:41:39,800
insist that I'm sick?

591
00:42:26,318 --> 00:42:30,756
♪The night stretches long,
like an endless hallway♪

592
00:42:32,118 --> 00:42:37,275
♪Without moonlight
or a god to guide the way♪

593
00:42:37,912 --> 00:42:42,783
♪Memories drip
within the center of my heart♪

594
00:42:43,038 --> 00:42:47,802
♪Burning you away,
leaving only emptiness♪

595
00:42:48,009 --> 00:42:50,821
♪The distorted truth♪

596
00:42:50,999 --> 00:42:56,584
♪Is tampered with,
buried, and forgotten♪

597
00:42:59,233 --> 00:43:05,147
♪Beyond the embers,
the wound remains warm♪

598
00:43:05,313 --> 00:43:10,098
♪It lights up again♪

599
00:43:10,827 --> 00:43:16,460
♪Whose hands♪

600
00:43:16,715 --> 00:43:20,039
♪Are pulling the strings?♪

601
00:43:20,196 --> 00:43:22,623
♪Who stands at the end of the lie?♪

602
00:43:22,632 --> 00:43:28,113
♪Behind the mask♪

603
00:43:28,466 --> 00:43:31,746
♪Whose softness♪

604
00:43:32,036 --> 00:43:33,858
♪Has decayed?♪

605
00:43:33,958 --> 00:43:37,666
♪Lift the dust, feel it with your soul♪

606
00:43:37,668 --> 00:43:42,593
♪The chains of destiny
have long bound us♪

607
00:43:42,838 --> 00:43:45,598
♪To each other♪

608
00:43:46,072 --> 00:43:48,537
♪If you don't die, I won't stop♪

609
00:43:48,605 --> 00:43:51,384
♪Let's witness together♪

610
00:43:51,488 --> 00:43:54,667
♪The end♪
